---
title: Creamy Bison and Bacon Linguine with Mushrooms and Apple Spinach Salad
description: This creamy linguine dish is full of savoury umami notes from mushrooms and bison, with bacon adding another level of savoury flavour. A light and refreshing apple, spinach side salad is the perfect balance for the divinely rich cream sauce!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/linguines-cremeuses-au-bison-et-au-bacon-383873aa.jpg
